PersonalMission.Name: HT-3: Omnivorous
PersonalMission.Description: Prove that your tank can destroy an enemy vehicle of any type.
PersonalMission.Hint: Every type of vehicle employs its own unique tactics on the battlefield. For example, medium tanks can easily outflank opponents, heavy tanks will most likely meet enemies head-on, and tank destroyers will prefer to position themselves on hills or hide behind bushes.

Primary.Conditions: •  Destroy 4 enemy vehicles of 3 different types
